description: Modern and elegant south-facing 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home that offers abundant natural light from the floor-to-ceiling glass windows. The home is adorned with wide plank oak hardwood floors, an open-concept floor plan and kitchen with custom high gloss, white Italian cabinetry, Thermador appliances and quartz countertops. The home also includes an in-unit Bosch washer/dryer and views of the pool and outdoor terrace, spa-like marble bathroom and spacious walk-in closet in the primary bedroom. The building amenities are the finest in the Seaport and include: 24-hour concierge, doorman, 24-hour valet parking, 1 indoor pool, 2 outdoor pools, hot tub, Sky Lounge with patio, state-of-the-art fitness center including indoor sports court, golf simulator and yoga studio, lounge with fireplace, library, private dining and wine room, and outdoor terraces with grill stations and fire pits. The Seaport is ideally located in walking distance to the Financial District and easy access to the highways
